originalText.text: Rachel was a pleasure to work with from day one. Not only did she simplify the daunting process of purchasing a Park Avenue co-op, she was available day or night. She absolutely knows the market and was a great coordinator between seller/sellers broker, the legal team and the board package aggregator. And she is very cool. If I purchase another property in the future I will definitely do so through Rachel.

originalText.text: We can't speak highly enough of our experience with Rachel White. We were first-time homebuyers in New York City with very little knowledge about how to find the right place for our daughter. She is honest and hands-on, and did a wonderful job answering our many questions. She helped us find the perfect apartment for our daughter, in a great building and a wonderful location.

originalText.text: Rachel White is a supreme realtor. She has a knack for getting to know her clients' wants and needs very well on the journey of searching for a home. Knowledge of her clients' day to day life and how they operate as humans helps to narrow down the process of finding the one place to call home in New York City. The market in Manhattan can be filled with seemingly endless listings and long lists of pros & cons. Rachel was very kind, patient, and generous with her time. She is an absolute dream to work with!!

originalText.text: Rachel White was great in helping my husband and me find our long term home to buy in NYC. She  knew the area well and had a great understanding of the different openings, listings and many of the brokers in the neighborhood. She made the process as seamless as it could be and I'd recommend her to anyone looking to buy in new york!

originalText.text: I am sitting in our new apartment watching the sun rise over the East River.   Rachel White showed us exactly what we were looking for in a  NYC apartment:  a fantastic view in a pet friendly building with a parking garage.  And best of all: it didn't take long.  My  husband and I agree that this was definitely our easiest real estate purchase.
